胜的是‘天使的泪’！恭喜这六位同学获得了露营的机会和奖学金。”\r<br>　　“OH～耶！！”\u0018","author":"花仙子Gigi","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2ab4647a.RrrW19Gb9VgQDw0NIH5_3w&fr=pb","date":"2008-08-13 18:02","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":62,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"沙发,我的沙发..........","author":"荷宝依依","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.3c39b4e8.BVUdTca9tjE6WRg6JKYDLw&fr=pb","date":"2008-08-15 11:31","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":63,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"板凳也要�","author":"荷宝依依","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.3c39b4e8.BVUdTca9tjE6WRg6JKYDLw&fr=pb","date":"2008-08-15 11:31","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":64,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"快写！快快快快快快快快快快快！！！！！！！！�","author":"0单纯0女孩0","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.a92814a6.LTMOmrBQws-q1Sgw0Ou7Lw&fr=pb","date":"2008-08-15 12:24","ip":null,"old_image":"http://hiphotos.baidu.com/tianyingyide/pic/item/98df0f0113b61b14738da5f8.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":65,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"咋不是冥羽心和幻�","author":"60.160.252.*","author_link":null,"date":"2008-08-15 12:26","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":67,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"ddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddd","author":"222.56.131.*","author_link":null,"date":"2008-08-15 14:21","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":68,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"加油","author":"舒橙","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.96ec3cd3.EEMTdj92rlg9RDlOIOzLNA?t=1567589064&fr=pb","date":"2008-08-15 16:09","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":69,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】七色光","content":"ddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddddd","author":"60.160.252.*","author_link":null,"date":"2008-08-16 12:08","ip":null,"old_image":"http://www.24kqq.com/upload/qimages/sz/33/845fbb1e-0f20-43ac-bbf1-8639f4132789.gif","user_sign_image